text: Animbiigoo Zaagi'igan Anishinaabek First Nation is an Ojibwe First Nation in northwestern Ontario. It has a reserve on Partridge Lake called Lake Nipigon Indian Reserve within the town of Greenstone. It is a member of Waaskiinaysay Ziibi Inc. ==References== Category:Ojibwe governments Category:Ojibwe reserves in Ontario Category:Communities in Thunder Bay District
